#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:2
msgid "Web Frontend"
msgstr "Web 前端"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:4
msgid ""
"DeePAW provides an online web application that allows users to perform "
"charge density predictions and visualization directly in the browser, "
"without writing any code."
msgstr "DeePAW 提供在线 Web 应用，用户可在浏览器中直接完成电荷密度预测与可视化，无需编写任何代码。"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:6
msgid "Access URL: **https://deepaw.tech**"
msgstr "访问地址：**https://deepaw.tech**"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:8
msgid ""
"The locally deployed version is accessible via ``http://localhost:3000`` "
"(local) or remotely through an SSH tunnel."
msgstr "本地部署版本在本机可通过 ``http://localhost:3000`` 访问，也可通过 SSH 隧道远程访问。"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:11
msgid "Login and Registration"
msgstr "登录与注册"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:13
msgid ""
"First-time users must register an account. An invitation code is required "
"during registration."
msgstr "首次使用者需注册账号，注册时必须提供邀请码。"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:15
msgid "DeePAW Login Page"
msgstr "DeePAW 登录页"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:19
msgid ""
"Login page: DeePAW branding on the left, login/registration form on the "
"right"
msgstr "登录页面左侧为 DeePAW 品牌，右侧为登录/注册表单"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:21
msgid "Enter your username, password, and email address"
msgstr "输入用户名、密码和电子邮件地址"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:22
msgid "Enter the invitation code (default: ``deepawdeepaw``)"
msgstr "输入邀请码（默认：``deepawdeepaw``）"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:23
msgid ""
"After successful registration, you will be redirected to the main interface "
"automatically"
msgstr "注册成功后，系统会自动跳转至主界面"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:25
msgid ""
"Existing users can log in by entering their username and password directly. "
"If you forget your password, it can be reset via email verification code."
msgstr "已有用户可直接使用用户名和密码登录。若忘记密码，可通过邮箱验证码重置。"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:28
msgid "Main Interface Layout"
msgstr "主界面布局"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:30
msgid ""
"After logging in, the main interface is displayed. The top navigation bar "
"contains two view-switching buttons:"
msgstr "登录后展示主界面，顶部导航栏包含两个视图切换按钮："

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:32
msgid "**Predictions**: Prediction workspace (default view)"
msgstr "**Predictions**：预测工作区（默认视图）"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:33
msgid "**My Files**: File and history management"
msgstr "**My Files**：文件及历史管理"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:35
msgid ""
"The currently logged-in username and a disconnect button are shown in the "
"upper-right corner."
msgstr "右上角显示当前登录用户名及退出按钮"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:38
msgid "Prediction Workspace (Predictions)"
msgstr "预测工作区（Predictions）"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:40
msgid "The prediction workspace uses a three-panel layout:"
msgstr "预测工作区采用三栏布局："

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:42
msgid "Prediction Workspace - File Upload and Parameter Configuration"
msgstr "预测工作区——文件上传与参数配置"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:46
msgid ""
"Prediction workspace interface: left panel shows GPU cluster status, center "
"panel shows file upload and task configuration, right panel shows the "
"visualization area"
msgstr "预测工作区界面：左侧显示 GPU 集群状态，中心显示文件上传和任务配置，右侧展示可视化区域"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:49
msgid "Left Panel: GPU Cluster Status"
msgstr "左侧面板：GPU 集群状态"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:51
msgid "Displays the real-time operating status of each GPU:"
msgstr "实时显示每块 GPU 的运行状态："

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:53
msgid "GPU name and index"
msgstr "GPU 名称和索引"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:54
msgid "VRAM usage (used / total in MB)"
msgstr "显存使用情况（已用/总计，单位 MB）"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:55
msgid "GPU utilization (%)"
msgstr "GPU 利用率（%）"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:56
msgid "Temperature"
msgstr "温度"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:57
msgid "Status indicator (idle/busy)"
msgstr "状态指示（空闲/忙碌）"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:59
msgid "Data is refreshed automatically every 5 seconds via WebSocket."
msgstr "数据通过 WebSocket 每 5 秒自动刷新。"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:62
msgid "Center Panel: Prediction Task Configuration"
msgstr "中间面板：预测任务配置"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:64
msgid "**Upload Structure Files**"
msgstr "**上传结构文件**"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:66
msgid ""
"Click the upload area to select files. Supported formats include CIF, VASP, "
"XYZ, PDB, and 14 others (15 formats total), as well as ZIP/TAR archives. The"
" grid dimensions nx, ny, and nz must be specified at upload time."
msgstr ""
"点击上传区域选择文件。支持 CIF、VASP、XYZ、PDB 等 15 种结构文件格式以及 ZIP/TAR 压缩包。上传时需填写网格尺寸 "
"nx、ny、nz。"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:68
msgid ""
"Alternatively, click \"Load Demo\" to quickly load the built-in "
"demonstration database."
msgstr "亦可点击 \"Load Demo\" 快速加载内置示例数据库。"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:70
msgid "**Submit Prediction**"
msgstr "**提交预测**"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:72
msgid "Select the structure ID range (start_id ~ end_id)"
msgstr "选择结构 ID 范围（start_id ~ end_id）"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:73
msgid "Click the submit button"
msgstr "点击提交按钮"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:74
msgid ""
"Tasks enter the GPU queue; each task card displays its status in real time:"
msgstr "任务进入 GPU 队列，每个任务卡实时显示状态："

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:76
msgid "Grey: pending"
msgstr "灰色：待处理"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:77
msgid "Blue: processing"
msgstr "蓝色：处理中"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:78
msgid "Green: completed"
msgstr "绿色：已完成"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:79
msgid "Red: failed"
msgstr "红色：失败"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:82
msgid "Right Panel: Visualization"
msgstr "右侧面板：可视化"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:84
msgid ""
"Once a task is complete, click its task card to view the prediction results "
"in the right panel. Two visualization modes are available:"
msgstr "任务完成后，点击对应任务卡在右侧面板查看预测结果。提供两种可视化模式："

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:86
msgid "**2D Slice (Slice)**"
msgstr "**2D Slice（切片）**"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:88
msgid ""
"A two-dimensional charge density slice along a specified Miller index (hkl) "
"plane:"
msgstr "沿指定 Miller 指数 (hkl) 平面生成二维电荷密度切片："

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:90
msgid "2D Charge Density Slice Visualization"
msgstr "二维电荷密度切片可视化"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:94
msgid ""
"2D slice view: heatmap of charge density distribution along the (hkl) plane,"
" with optional contour overlay and Gaussian blur"
msgstr "二维切片视图：展示 (hkl) 平面上的电荷密度热图，可叠加等高线并使用高斯模糊"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:96
msgid "Select the slice direction (h, k, l)"
msgstr "选择切片方向（h、k、l）"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:97
msgid "Adjust the slice distance (distance)"
msgstr "调节切片距离（distance）"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:98
msgid "Gaussian blur smoothing supported"
msgstr "支持高斯模糊平滑"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:99
msgid "Contour overlay display supported"
msgstr "支持等高线叠加显示"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:100
msgid "Viridis colormap"
msgstr "Viridis 颜色映射"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:102
msgid "**3D Isosurface (Isosurface)**"
msgstr "**3D Isosurface（等值面）**"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:104
msgid ""
"Interactive three-dimensional isosurface rendering powered by Plotly.js:"
msgstr "基于 Plotly.js 的交互式三维等值面渲染："

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:106
msgid "3D Charge Density Isosurface Visualization"
msgstr "三维电荷密度等值面可视化"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:110
msgid ""
"3D isosurface view: interactive three-dimensional charge density rendering "
"showing the unit cell boundary and lattice parameters"
msgstr "三维等值面视图：交互式渲染电荷密度，展示晶胞边界与晶格参数"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:112
msgid "Click and drag to rotate the view"
msgstr "点击拖拽可旋转视图"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:113
msgid "Scroll to zoom"
msgstr "滚轮缩放"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:114
msgid "Adjustable isosurface threshold (ISO MIN/MAX)"
msgstr "可调节等值面阈值（ISO MIN/MAX）"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:115
msgid "Adjustable resolution and number of isosurface levels"
msgstr "可调节分辨率与等值面层数"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:116
msgid ""
"Displays the unit cell boundary (gold wireframe) and lattice parameters (a, "
"b, c, alpha, beta, gamma)"
msgstr "显示晶胞边界（金色线框）及晶格参数（a、b、c、alpha、beta、gamma）"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:119
msgid "File Management (My Files)"
msgstr "文件管理（My Files）"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:121
msgid ""
"Switch to the \"My Files\" view to manage uploaded files and prediction "
"history:"
msgstr "切换至 \"My Files\" 页面管理已上传文件和预测历史："

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:123
msgid "File Management and Result Storage Page"
msgstr "文件管理与结果存储页面"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:127
msgid ""
"My Files view: uploaded file list and prediction history, showing download "
"status and expiration information"
msgstr "My Files 视图显示上传文件列表及预测历史，包含下载状态和过期信息"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:129
msgid "**Uploaded File List**"
msgstr "**已上传文件列表**"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:131
msgid "File name and upload time"
msgstr "文件名与上传时间"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:132
msgid "Days since upload"
msgstr "上传后天数"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:133
msgid "Download status (available / expired)"
msgstr "下载状态（可用/已过期）"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:134
msgid "Files are available for download for 3 days"
msgstr "文件在 3 天内可下载"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:136
msgid "**Prediction History**"
msgstr "**预测历史**"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:138
msgid "Task ID and creation time"
msgstr "任务 ID 与创建时间"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:139
msgid "CHGCAR file path"
msgstr "CHGCAR 文件路径"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:140
msgid "Download status and expiration"
msgstr "下载状态与过期时间"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:143
msgid "Performance Tips"
msgstr "性能提示"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:145
msgid "**3D Visualization Optimization**"
msgstr "**3D 可视化优化**"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:147
msgid ""
"For large CHGCAR files (grid > 48^3), it is recommended to preview at "
"reduced resolution first"
msgstr "对于大体积 CHGCAR 文件（网格 > 48^3），建议先使用降低分辨率预览"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:148
msgid ""
"Reducing the number of isosurface levels improves browser rendering "
"performance"
msgstr "降低等值面层数有助于提升浏览器渲染性能"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:149
msgid ""
"Raising the ISO MIN threshold to display only high-density regions reduces "
"the number of rendered polygons"
msgstr "提升 ISO MIN 阈值仅显示高密度区域，可减少渲染多边形数量"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:151
msgid "**Browser Compatibility**"
msgstr "**浏览器兼容性**"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:153
msgid "Chrome / Edge (Chromium-based) is recommended"
msgstr "建议使用基于 Chromium 的 Chrome / Edge 浏览器"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:154
msgid "WebGL support is required (for Plotly 3D rendering)"
msgstr "需要支持 WebGL（用于 Plotly 3D 渲染）"

#: ../../platform/web_frontend.rst:155
msgid "A screen resolution of >= 1920x1080 is recommended"
msgstr "推荐屏幕分辨率不低于 1920×1080"
